    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cosmic Kitchen takes a twist on traditional cooking games, but mixes it up with cooking in space! Feed hungry space monsters as you travel the galaxy on an adventure to become the best space chef in the cosmos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think fast and grab food as it flies into orbit. Take advantage of the cosmos by using planets and the solar system to help prepare your food!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Available in the demo: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 playable galaxies </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roughly 40 minutes of gameplay!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prepare food the space way!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266490/extras/cf94a647d4005a3f7d8999bd3dea484a.poster.avif?t=1731364699\" width=554 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266490/extras/cf94a647d4005a3f7d8999bd3dea484a.webm?t=1731364699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266490/extras/cf94a647d4005a3f7d8999bd3dea484a.mp4?t=1731364699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sun = Cooking</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Water Planet = Boiling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space Vortex = Mixing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ring Planet = Chopping</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And many more ways to prep food!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll never run out of space in this kitchen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Feed Monsters!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266490/extras/8275de0c3efc20a6527a8532c7a3c371.poster.avif?t=1731364699\" width=800 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266490/extras/8275de0c3efc20a6527a8532c7a3c371.webm?t=1731364699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266490/extras/8275de0c3efc20a6527a8532c7a3c371.mp4?t=1731364699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep up with the demands of hungry space monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the Galaxies!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266490/extras/a7d0e87ab3840c84abde7fa11c8be85b.poster.avif?t=1731364699\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266490/extras/a7d0e87ab3840c84abde7fa11c8be85b.webm?t=1731364699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266490/extras/a7d0e87ab3840c84abde7fa11c8be85b.mp4?t=1731364699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are multiple galaxies planned, each galaxy will have different recipes and new ways of preparing food! </p>",
